      {
        "subtopic": "Finding Rate",
        "content": "**Q:** If the SI on ₹1500 for 3 years is ₹270, find the rate.\n\n**Solution:**\nSI = (P × R × T)/100\n270 = (1500 × R × 3)/100\n270 = 45R ⇒ R = 6%\n\n**Answer:** 6% per annum"
